Package: usRds
Type: Package
Title: A Package to Automate Processing and Access to the USRDS
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(
        person("Vagish", "Hemmige", email = "vahemmig@montefiore.org", role = c("aut", "cre")),
        person("Cervera Hernandez", "Miguel", email = "Miguel.Cerverahernandez@SanfordHealth.org", role = "ctb")
    )
Description: 
    Provides tools to simplify access to and processing of data from the United States Renal Data System (USRDS). 
    Supports multiple raw formats (SAS, CSV, Parquet), automated file detection, optional value and variable labeling 
    using USRDS appendices, and functions to filter claims data by diagnosis and procedure codes. Designed for 
    reproducible, large-scale cohort construction and longitudinal analysis.
